	   <tr><td colspan=2>Can't get my pet to attack the selected target. I am an 11th lvl mage. I have a hot key which is programmed as /pet attack. Why does it attack a different target than the one I choose? H.E.L.P. Please!<br><br>Majhik<br>Mage of the 11th Order<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
