	   <tr><td colspan=2>It might be lag, you may not be close enough to the target and it looks like your clicking on the right on.&nbsp;&nbsp;Also, if your in a group and the selected monster is not hitting your pet but the one behind it with no one else on it is, your pet will turn on that one.  If grouped make a hotkey /assist &lt;tank name&gt; or whoever the puller is.  Wait until they start to beat on something then send pet in after assisting.<br><br>You can also set up hot keys like this:<br><br>/assist &lt;tank or puller name&gt;<br>/pet attack<br><br>this will cause you to assist whatever they are hitting and also send pet in at same time.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
