	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Pets can be such unpredictable little creatures if we leave them to their own devices. But do we not cherish our faithful, gallant defenders?&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>If I had not given my pet the "/pet follow me" command, the pet would invariably attack whatever MOB was nearest to it. Proximity or poor targetting was not the issue, my lack of connection to my pet, via the "follow me" command was. Since learning this lesson, my pet always attacks just what I tell it to or that which attacks me.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
